item.title: Marsha Blackburn biograph
item.description: Senator Marsha Blackburn Biograph Senator Marsha Blackburn is an American politician and businesswoman. He has been serving as a senior US Senator from Tennessee under the Republicans since 2018. She was a member of the State Senate from 1999 to 2003. She was also a member of the US House of Representatives from 2003 to 2019. Marsha was born in Laurel, Mississippi, on June 6, 1952. She was a beauty pageant winner back at high school.
